This chunk is part of the `DistancePhasedNode` class implementation, which manages dynamic regions or zones defined by distance-based phases in a 3D environment. The methods handle phase transitions (via `setPhase()`) and collision detection events (`__getEnterEvent()` and `__getExitEvent()`) to enable smooth zone changes for objects or characters moving through the scene.

